dc_title_s: Right of Way (ROW) Kenosha County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: This data layer represents right of ways (ROW) for Kenosha County, Wisconsin in 2014.[Kenosha County Cadastral Line Features. Contains all lines for COX - Condominium Boundary Lines, CSX - CSM Boundary Lines, EAX - Easement Lines, PLX - Parcel Lines, RWX - ROW Lines, SDX - Subdivision Boundary Lines, TMX - Tie Mark Lines, TRX - Text Related Leader Lines.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
